{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述三阵赌局的高潮与对峙。卜鹰以空手接住卫天鹏全力一刀，弹断其长刀，展现虽负伤仍不可轻敌的恐怖实力。搜魂手在前两阵败北后胆寒不敢出手，小方欲以自身为筹码换取众人安全，被卜鹰坚决拒绝。柳分分亮出底牌：营地外有七十名精兵和一顶神秘轿子，以此要挟卜鹰答应查看货物、带走小方两个条件。卜鹰拒绝交出小方，豪迈回应愿意赌到底，双方陷入僵持。本章集中展现卜鹰的霸气与义气、柳分分的智谋与狠辣，以及小方的侠义性格。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "这一刀还不够快，这把刀也不够快。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然已负伤，可是你们也不该低估我的，因为我还没有死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "只要你不死，就没有人能击败你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "直到现在还没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_sou_hun_shou",
      "text": "现在，只剩下你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_sou_hun_shou",
      "text": "三阵赌输赢，你们已败了两阵，你是不是想拼一拼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sou_hun_shou",
      "text": "这个人，是我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这个人当然是你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "只要他出手，三招之内，必将死在你的剑下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "刚才你说是十招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在已不同了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在他的胆已寒，气已馁，你要杀他，已经用不着十招。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_sou_hun_shou",
      "text": "只可惜他绝不敢出手的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他当然不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "无论斗智斗力，卜大老板都无人能及。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "但是智者千虑，也难免会有所失。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我们虽然败了，但是还没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "只要我一声令下，他们就会冲过来，片刻间这里就将横尸遍地，血流成河。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "text": "你们外面还有轿子，轿子当然不会是空的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我们当然不会抬一顶空轿子来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道你一直想看看轿子里究竟有什么？但是不到最后关头时，我们是绝不会让你看到的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "现在还不到最后关头，因为我们还有赌注，还可以跟你们赌一赌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "只看卜大老板是不是愿意用你这么多子弟伙伴的性命，来跟我们赌。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我知道你很难下决定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "不到最后关头，我们也同样不愿意跟你赌，只要你答应我们两点小小的要求，我们立刻就走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我们想看看你的货，每一包都要看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "黄金既然不在这里，你就让我们看看又何妨？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我们是想把这个人带走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "他跟你非亲非故，你何必为他跟我们拼命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "text": "你们的要求听来好像并不过分。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "非但不过分，而且很合理。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我知道你一定会答应的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我愿意跟他们走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "随时都可以走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我明白你的意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你一向不愿连累别人，更不愿无辜者为你而死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我本来就不该留在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是你忘了一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你留下来，是我要你留下来的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我既然要你留下来，谁也不能带你走。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "speaker_name": "柳分分",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你真的要跟我们赌一赌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_liu_fen_fen",
      "text": "现在你们已经可以下令，要你们那七十位久经训练，百战不死的战士冲过来了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 172
    }
  ],
